@fhirBaseUrl = http://localhost:8080/fhir

### Create Patient
POST {{fhirBaseUrl}}/Patient
Content-Type: application/fhir+json
Accept: application/fhir+json

< ../examples/fhir/patient-basic.json

### Read Patient
# Replace PATIENT_ID after the create response.
GET {{fhirBaseUrl}}/Patient/1001
Accept: application/fhir+json

### Negative case: endpoint/resourceType mismatch
POST {{fhirBaseUrl}}/Patient
Content-Type: application/fhir+json
Accept: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Observation",
  "status": "final",
  "code": {
    "text": "Synthetic negative test"
  }
}

### Negative case: invalid FHIR date lexical value

POST {{fhirBaseUrl}}/Patient
Content-Type: application/fhir+json
Accept: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Patient",
  "birthDate": "12/03/1975"
}